name: .DBS File Extension
summary: Learn about .DBS files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Database file created by SQLBase, an embedded database solution for business applications; stores structured data and tracks changes to the data in a ".log" file; often used for storing data for small desktop programs or mobile applications.

content: Gupta Technologies, the original developers of SQLBase, renamed to Centura Software in the 1990s. In 2006, Centura Software was acquired by Unify Corporation.
